dct_description_sm: Pennsylvania Geological Survey. (2nd survey) Final Report 1891-95. Companion text: Pennsylvania Geological Survey (2d:1874-1890). Final report ordered by Legislature, 1891. A summary description of the geology of Pennsylvania / J. P. Lesley. Harrisburg : Pennsylvania Geological Survey. 1892-95. Final report 1891-1895. 3 vol. in 4 and atlas : 2588p. 25pl.
